 \"3D printing withFormula 1-style technology\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not a sense thatTeam GBhave somehow got the jump on their rivals in that regard - with the other powerhouses of the sport having taken similar approaches.\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 812, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 669}, {\"ngram\": \"GBhave\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 685}, {\"ngram\": \"the jump\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 706}, {\"ngram\": \"their rivals\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 722}, {\"ngram\": \"that regard\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 737}, {\"ngram\": \"the other powerhouses\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 766}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"similar approaches\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But British bikes havealready crossed the line to one goldat theParis Olympicswith more set to follow in the coming days.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 935, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 818, \"end\": 825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9945041248387546, \"rank\": 0.005284452020550312, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 860}, {\"ngram\": \"one goldat\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 874}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympicswith\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 896}, {\"ngram\": \"the coming days\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bikes used between the sprint and endurance programmes are effectively the same, although the handlebars are wholly different when it comes to assuming the pursuing position.\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The bikes\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 946}, {\"ngram\": \"the sprint and endurance programmes\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 995}, {\"ngram\": \"the handlebars\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"the pursuing position\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The main area of change on the bikes is the seat post, which basically is split to create less disruption of airflow around the legs and therefore more aerodynamic.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1281, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The main area\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1130}, {\"ngram\": \"change\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"the bikes\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"the seat post\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"less disruption\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1222}, {\"ngram\": \"airflow\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1233}, {\"ngram\": \"the legs\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There had been tweaks to the handlebars too, which further enhances the riders' bike and body position, and there are new-for-Paris skinsuits.\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tweaks\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"the handlebars\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1322}, {\"ngram\": \"the riders' bike\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"body position\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year Keely Hodgkinson reveals Grand Slam Track decision and 2025 ambitions The best destinations and activities to book this winter Trying to work out the advantage the collective changes gives to British riders is hard to quantify but it starts with a psychological one according to six-time Olympic champion Chris Hoy.\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1558, \"end\": 1574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", 