 final piece\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"the jigsaw\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was like an additional feel-good factor.\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an additional feel-good factor\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You were in the form of your life, rested, fresh, tapered, this was just the latest in the culmination of all the pieces of the jigsaw.\\\"\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the form\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2058}, {\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2071}, {\"ngram\": \"the culmination\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2140}, {\"ngram\": \"all the pieces\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2158}, {\"ngram\": \"the jigsaw\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he stresses this is not like Max Verstappen in a Red Bull and Alex Albon in a Williams in terms of the disparity of the technology.\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2311, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2209, \"end\": 2223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Verstappen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Max Verstappen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Verstappen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Verstappen\"}, {\"begin\": 2242, \"end\": 2252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Albon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Albon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Albon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Albon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a Red Bull\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2237}, {\"ngram\": \"a Williams\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2266}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2275}, {\"ngram\": \"the disparity\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"the technology\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some people might say it's just like Formula 1 and it's the bikes win the medals but the answer to that is 'no',\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some people\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2325}, {\"ngram\": \"Formula\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"the bikes\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2379}, {\"ngram\": \"the medals\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"the answer\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's part of the tools of the trade and you want the best tools you possibly can which is why teams invest.\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2447}, {\"ngram\": \"the tools\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2460}, {\"ngram\": \"the trade\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2473}, {\"ngram\": \"the best tools\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2501}, {\"ngram\": \"teams\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And it's hard to say which team has the best.\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2593, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"which team\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unless you line them all up with the same rider in a wind tunnel, you do not know.\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2676, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same rider\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2641}, {\"ngram\": \"a wind tunnel\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Plus, the advantage of a nation's skinsuit can vary from one rider to the next with the different body shapes.\\\"\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the advantage\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2696}, {\"ngram\": \"a nation's skinsuit\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"one rider\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2743}, {\"ngram\": \"the different body shapes\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 27